text.a: Encounter between a subject of care and a health systemencounter

Summary information or comments about the clinical management of the patient, and the prognosis of diagnoses or problems identified during the healthcare encounter. It may also include health-related information pertinent to the patient, and a clinical interpretation of relevant investigations and observations performed on the patient (including pathology and diagnostic imaging)clinicalSynopsis
